articles.title: Moldovans cast ballots in a tense election plagued by Russian interference claims - CNN
articles.description: Moldovans are heading to the polls to cast ballots in a tense parliamentary election plagued by claims of Russian interference, a vote seen as a choice between integration with the European Union or a drift back into Moscow’s fold.
